		"name": "QR Order API v2.0",
		"description": "Complete collection for QR Ordering System with Role-Based Access Control.\n\n### Authentication\nUse the **Authentification > Login** request to authenticate. The `token` variable will be automatically updated with the login response.\n\n### Roles\n- **SUPER_ADMIN**: Manage restaurants and plans.\n- **OWNER**: Manage their own restaurant, menus, and staff.\n- **MANAGER/STAFF**: Manage orders and restaurant operations.\n- **CUSTOMER**: View menus and place orders.",
